quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  17,78,Chita mapemphero kuyambira nthawi yopendekera dzuwakufikirausikundipowerenga Koranim’mapemphero a m’mbandakucha. Ndithudi kuwerenga Korani nthawi ya m’mbandakucha kumachitilidwa umboni
  17,79,"Ndipo m’kati mwa usiku, pemphera ndi kuwerenga Korani ndi mapemphero oonjezera kwa iwe. Mwina Ambuye wako angadzakuike pamalo wotamandika"
  17,80,"Nena, “Ambuye ndilowetseni kulowa kwa bwino ndipo nditulutseni mwaubwino. Ndipo ndipatseni kuchokera kwa Inu mphamvu yondithandiza.”"
  17,81,"Nena, “Choonadi chadza ndipo bodza latha. Ndithudi bodza liyenera kutha.”"
  17,82,"Ndipo titumiza kuchokera m’Korani mankhwala ochiza ndiponso chisoni kwa onse okhulupirira, ndipo imaonjezera kwa anthu osakhulupirira chionongeko"
  17,83,"Ndipo tikam’patsa munthu zokoma zathu, iye amatembenuka ndi kuchita mwano ndipo amakhala kutali ndi njira yoyenera. Ndipo zikam’peza zoipa amakhala wotaya mtima kwambiri"
  17,84,"Nena, “Munthu aliyense amachita molingana ndi chikhalidwe chake koma Ambuye wanu amadziwa yemwe watsogozedwa bwino panjira yachilungamo.”"